      <title>泰德·克鲁兹与民主党挑战者在边境、堕胎、坎昆问题上展开激烈较量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ted-cruz-jousts-with-democratic-challenger-on-border-abortion-cancun</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党参议员泰德·克鲁兹与民主党挑战者美国众议员科林·奥尔雷德在争夺德克萨斯州参议院席位的唯一一场辩论中，就边境安全、堕胎和经济等问题发生了冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ted-cruz-jousts-with-democratic-challenger-on-border-abortion-cancun</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 02:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
